---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Benchmark Metrics Definition"; // Will be replaced by translation
const activeNav = "metrics";
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} activeNav={activeNav}>
  <main class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 py-12 md:py-16 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <header class="mb-10 md:mb-12 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4" data-lang-key="metrics_page_title">Benchmark Metrics</h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-lang-key="metrics_page_subtitle">
          用于故事可视化的综合评估指标，评估一致性、依从性、质量、多样性和人类感知。
        </p>
      </header>

      <section id="metrics-definitions" class="space-y-8 md:space-y-10">

        <!-- 1. Character Consistency (CRef) -->
        <div class="metric-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400">
                <path d="M4.5 6.375a4.125 4.125 0 1 1 8.25 0 4.125 4.125 0 0 1-8.25 0ZM14.25 8.625a3.375 3.375 0 1 1 6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1-6.75 0ZM1.5 19.125a7.125 7.125 0 0 1 14.25 0v.003l-.001.119a.75.75 0 0 1-.363.63 13.067 13.067 0 0 1-6.761 1.873c-2.472 0-4.786-.684-6.76-1.873a.75.75 0 0 1-.364-.63l-.001-.122ZM17.25 19.128l-.001.144a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.53 1.064 3.005 3.005 0 0 1-1.5 1.434 9.07 9.07 0 0 1-2.55-.042 9.07 9.07 0 0 1-2.55.042c-.928 0-1.79-.304-2.499-1.434a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.531-1.064l-.002-.144a3.375 3.375 0 0 1 3.375-3.375h3.75a3.375 3.375 0 0 1 3.375 3.375Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100" data-lang-key="cref_title">1. 角色一致性 (CRef)</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mt-1 text-base leading-relaxed" data-lang-key="cref_desc">评估角色在图像序列中是否保持外观一致。重点关注角色身份特征的自相似性和与参考图像的交叉相似性。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_accs">aCCS (平均角色相似度)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_accs_desc">使用CLIP图像特征计算跨帧的角色相似度（参考Theatregen, Story-Adapter）。适用于一般角色。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_face">ArcFace / AdaFace</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_face_desc">专用于真实人物的面部识别模型，提取面部特征用于相似度计算。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_ccip">CCIP</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_ccip_desc">适用于动漫风格角色的一致性评估，通常需要图像中单个角色的检测。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_confusion">多人混淆度</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_confusion_desc">衡量在多角色场景中，模型区分不同角色的能力，避免身份错配。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_grounding">Grounding DINO + 相似度</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_grounding_desc">首先使用 Grounding DINO 根据文本描述检测并裁剪出主要角色，然后计算其与参考图像在CLIP、FID或DreamSim等特征空间上的相似度。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_dreamsim">DreamSim 相似度</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_dreamsim_desc">一种跨模态的细粒度匹配指标，用于评估生成图像与参考图像在感知上的相似性。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_vbench">VBench 角色追踪</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_vbench_desc">将视频领域中评估角色一致性的方法应用于图像序列，追踪角色在序列中的稳定性。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_charf1">Char-F1 / Char-Acc</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_charf1_desc">使用预训练的角色分类器识别生成图像中的角色，并与真实标签（Ground Truth）比较，计算F1分数或准确率。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" data-lang-key="cref_sub_vlm">VLM 验证</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1" data-lang-key="cref_sub_vlm_desc">利用视觉语言模型（VLM）对比生成图像中的角色与人工标注的真实角色信息，进行一致性验证。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Style Consistency (SRef) -->
        <div class="metric-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">
                <path d="M11.03 2.59a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.94 0l7.5 6.363a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 .53 1.144V19.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-3a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5v-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H8.25a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v3.03a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-3a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5v-9.263a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 .53-1.144l7.5-6.363Z" />
                <path d="M19.5 9.75V15.75h-4.5V9.75h4.5Z" />
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9 2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V4.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75ZM15.75 3.75a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0V4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V3.75Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                <path d="M8.25 12.355a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25h3a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V15a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H9a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75v-2.645Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100" data-lang-key="sref_title">2. 风格一致性 (SRef)</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mt-1 text-base leading-relaxed" data-lang-key="sref_desc">评估图像序列中的艺术风格是否保持一致，包括与参考图像的风格交叉相似性以及生成图像间的风格自相似性。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">CSD (CLIP 风格编码器距离)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">通过CSD-CLIP特征分析量化自相似性（生成图像内部）和交叉相似性（生成图像与参考图像之间）。首先用CLIP视觉编码器提取特征，然后通过CSD层分离内容与风格特征，最后计算风格特征嵌入之间的余弦相似度。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">VLM 评分</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">利用如Qwen或GPT-4o等视觉语言模型对生成图像序列的风格一致性进行打分。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">ArtFID</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">一种针对艺术风格的FID（Fréchet Inception Distance）变体，用于评估生成图像在艺术美学上的真实感和多样性。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">频率分析 / VGG 距离</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">通过分析图像的频率域特征或使用VGG网络提取的深层特征间的距离，来评估风格的相似性，属于更高级的探索性方法。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Prompt Adherence -->
        <div class="metric-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.625 1.5H9a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25v1.875c0 .097.009.19.026.282A5.96 5.96 0 0 1 14.25 6c.39 0 .772.035 1.148.102.097-.017.19-.026.282-.026V3.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 1.5h3.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v20.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125H2.625A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.5 22.875V2.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3ZM9 12.75a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h.008a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H9Zm.75 2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h3a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-3a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75ZM9.75 9a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75V12a.75.75 0 0 0 .75.75h5.25a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V9.75a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H9.75Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                <path d="M14.25 7.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3 0V9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100" data-lang-key="prompt_title">3. 提示依从性</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mt-1 text-base leading-relaxed" data-lang-key="prompt_desc">评估生成的图像与故事板描述（提示）的吻合程度，包括角色互动、拍摄方法、出场角色数量准确性及个体行为。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">客观评估 - 实体存在 (VLM)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">使用VLM评估关键实体（物体、颜色、角色数量与描述、行为）是否按提示出现。特别是出场角色数量匹配度（OCCM），通过公式 `100 * exp(-|检测数-期望数| / (epsilon + 期望数))` 计算。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">客观评估 - 相机/镜头类型 (VLM)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">评估生成图像的拍摄方法（如长/中镜头，高/低角度）是否与故事板中的"镜头视角设计"一致。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">客观评估 - 环境一致性 (VLM)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">评估生成图像中的场景属性、时间、地点等是否与故事板中"场景描述"一致。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">主观评估 - 情感 / 氛围 (VLM)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">评估生成图像所传达的情感和氛围是否与提示中的描述（如角色互动、静态描述）相符。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">主观评估 - 动作 / 表情 (Grounding DINO + VLM)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">结合Grounding DINO进行角色分割后，利用VLM验证个体角色的动作和表情是否符合故事板中的"静态镜头描述"。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 4. Generation Quality -->
        <div class="metric-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-500 dark:text-amber-400">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.788 3.21c.448-1.077 1.976-1.077 2.424 0l2.082 5.006 5.404.434c1.164.093 1.636 1.545.749 2.305l-4.117 3.527 1.257 5.273c.271 1.136-.964 2.033-1.96 1.425L12 18.354 7.373 21.18c-.996.608-2.231-.29-1.96-1.425l1.257-5.273-4.117-3.527c-.887-.76-.415-2.212.749-2.305l5.404-.434 2.082-5.005Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100" data-lang-key="quality_title">4. 生成质量</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mt-1 text-base leading-relaxed" data-lang-key="quality_desc">评估生成图像的视觉质量和美学吸引力，以及是否存在"复制粘贴"参考图像的问题。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">美学评分 (aesthetic-predictor-v2-5)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">使用 Aesthetic Predictor V2.5 (基于SigLIP) 评估图像美感，分数范围1-10，高于5.5分通常认为质量优良。关注图像是否模糊、有噪点等。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">FID (Fréchet Inception Distance)</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">衡量生成图像与真实图像在特征空间分布上的相似性，常用于评估真实感图像的质量。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">PickScore</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">基于CLIP的图像质量评估模型，能预测人类对图像的偏好排名，反映生成图像的整体吸引力。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">复制粘贴检测</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">检测模型是否过度依赖或直接复制角色参考图像。对于单图输入模型，比较输出角色与输入图和备用参考图的相似度差异；多图输入模型此项不适用。</p>
            </div>
             <div class="sub-metric-item p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/60 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/80">
              <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium">退化分析</strong>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">分析生成质量是否随图像序列长度的增加而下降。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Diversity -->
        <div class="metric-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 6a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h12a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v12a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V6Zm4.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 0-3 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3Zm7.5-1.5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0Zm-7.5-4.5a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 0-3 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3Zm7.5-1.5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
